sequenceDiagram
    participant BIOS as BIOS/UEFI
    participant GRUB as GRUB
    participant Kernel as Linux Kernel
    participant systemd as systemd
    participant ASC as Volt ASC
    participant VKB as Kernel B
    participant VRMD as VRM
    participant DWP as DWP
    participant VGM as VGM
    participant VUM as VUM
    participant KA as Kernel A (Node)
    participant DM as Display Manager
    participant Electron as Electron Desktop

    BIOS->>GRUB: Boot ISO
    GRUB->>Kernel: Load vmlinuz + initrd
    Kernel->>systemd: Start init
    systemd->>ASC: volt-asc.service (oneshot)
    ASC-->>ASC: Detect hardware
    ASC-->>ASC: Generate config
    systemd->>VKB: volt-kernel-b.service
    VKB-->>VKB: Start Tesseract Engine
    systemd->>VRMD: volt-ram-manager.service
    systemd->>DWP: volt-worker-pool.service
    systemd->>VGM: volt-gpu-manager.service
    systemd->>VUM: volt-usb-manager.service
    systemd->>KA: volt-kernel.service (After=network)
    KA-->>KA: Start WS server :9999
    KA-->>KA: Init Volt Unifier
    systemd->>DM: lightdm + Xorg
    DM->>Electron: samaris-xsession
    Electron->>KA: WebSocket connect
    Note over Electron,KA: Desktop ready
